{"tid":1413793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遍地開花嘅真諦唔係輪流接力，係一齊上呀","createTime":"2019-08-05T10:58:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T10:59:06.000Z","uid":250508,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8dc08c033ee4dec9ca64b6b853fd6c24304ba09f","tid":1413793,"uid":250508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:58:16.000Z","msg":"今日三罷七區集會將狗力極度分散<br />\n佢哋根本連裝備都唔夠分<br />\n<br />\n射完一百幾十粒催淚之後義士同街坊都唔散 佢哋可以點？<br />\n縮返入狗署同老母個西度呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以遍地開花唔係輪流做 係全香港一齊嚟<br />\n分散警力之餘仲可以對經濟做成最大嘅衝突<br />\n一個區10萬人遊行= 一個區做唔倒生意<br />\n10個區一萬人遊行= 十 個 區 都 做 唔 倒 生 意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21fcf9bbdf40be92c401bb3f435339b03034496","tid":1413793,"uid":73565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:59:06.000Z","msg":"最好就今晚零被捕"}]}